      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="The creation and extension of the Material Master involve a series of steps that ensure the accurate and efficient handling of material data. The process begins with sending basic and classification view attributes to the translator and concludes with the replication of the material to downstream systems. Throughout the process, various checks, derivations, and validations are performed to maintain data integrity and accuracy."/>
